- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper may discuss machine learning techniques used in the detection and localization process.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possibility as the paper may discuss image processing techniques used in the detection and localization process.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper may discuss control systems used in the detection and localization process.
